<item>
            <title>[SYNAPSE-393] Convertion not complete when using SOAPUtils.convertSOAP11toSOAP12()</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SYNAPSE-393</link>
                <project id="12310201" key="SYNAPSE">Synapse</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When using org.apache.synapse.core.axis2.SOAPUtils.convertSOAP11toSOAP12() to convert a SOAP 1.1 message containing a SOAPFault to a SOAP 1.2 message, the method only converts the Envelope, the Header and the Body elements.&lt;br/&gt;
The Fault element is not converted ans its structure is not transformed into a SOAP 1.2 Fault structure.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Before using the method:&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;soapenv:Envelope xmlns:soapenv=&quot;http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/envelope/&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
   &amp;lt;soapenv:Body&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;soapenv:Fault&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
         &amp;lt;faultcode&amp;gt;soapenv:Client&amp;lt;/faultcode&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
         &amp;lt;faultstring&amp;gt;Erreur relative au referentiel des conventions. &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;Fichier de convention&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;lt;/faultstring&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
         &amp;lt;faultactor&amp;gt;Referentiel des Conventions.&amp;lt;/faultactor&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
         &amp;lt;detail&amp;gt;Il n&apos;y a pas de convention qui corresponde aux issuer, supplier et service&amp;lt;/detail&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;/soapenv:Fault&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
   &amp;lt;/soapenv:Body&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;/soapenv:Envelope&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;After using the method:&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;soapenv:Envelope xmlns:soapenv=&quot;http://www.w3.org/2003/05/soap-envelope&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
   &amp;lt;soapenv:Body&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;soapenv:Fault xmlns:soapenv=&quot;http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/envelope/&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
         &amp;lt;faultcode&amp;gt;soapenv:Client&amp;lt;/faultcode&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
         &amp;lt;faultstring&amp;gt;Erreur relative au referentiel des conventions. &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;Fichier de convention&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;lt;/faultstring&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
         &amp;lt;faultactor&amp;gt;Referentiel des Conventions.&amp;lt;/faultactor&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
         &amp;lt;detail&amp;gt;Il n&apos;y a pas de convention qui corresponde aux issuer, supplier et service&amp;lt;/detail&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;/soapenv:Fault&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
   &amp;lt;/soapenv:Body&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;/soapenv:Envelope&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It should be:&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;soapenv:Envelope xmlns:soapenv=&quot;http://www.w3.org/2003/05/soap-envelope&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
   &amp;lt;soapenv:Body&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;soapenv:Fault&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
         &amp;lt;soapenv:Code&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
            &amp;lt;soapenv:Value&amp;gt;soapenv:Client&amp;lt;/soapenv:Value&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
         &amp;lt;/soapenv:Code&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
         &amp;lt;soapenv:Reason&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
            &amp;lt;soapenv:Text&amp;gt;Erreur relative au referentiel des conventions. &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;Fichier de convention&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;lt;/soapenv:Text&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
         &amp;lt;/soapenv:Reason&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
         &amp;lt;soapenv:Role&amp;gt;Referentiel des Conventions.&amp;lt;/soapenv:Role&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
         &amp;lt;soapenv:Detail&amp;gt;Il n&apos;y a pas de convention qui corresponde aux issuer, supplier et service&amp;lt;/soapenv:Detail&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;/soapenv:Fault&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
   &amp;lt;/soapenv:Body&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;/soapenv:Envelope&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>OS: Windows XP SP2</environment>
